items.title: Pokémon-Shaped Cheeto Sells At Auction For Whopping $87,840
items.description: Sixty people attempted to buy the "Cheetozard," a Cheeto shaped like the beloved Pokémon Charizard, during an auction on Sunday.

items.title: Man Accused Of Swallowing $770K Worth Of Diamonds From Florida Tiffany's
items.description: Jaythan Gilder allegedly asked jailers, “Am I going to be charged with what’s in my stomach?”
